libs.content:
find_library( fftw_single_precision_libraries
    names fftw3f libfftw3f-3
    hints
        ${fftw_root}/lib
        ${fftw_root}/.libs
        ${fftw_root}
        $env{fftw_root}/lib
        $env{fftw_root}/.libs
        env fftw_root
    paths
        /usr/lib
        /usr/local/lib
    doc "fftw dynamic library"
)

find_library( fftw_double_precision_libraries
    names fftw3 libfftw3-3
    hints
        ${fftw_root}/lib
        ${fftw_root}/.libs
        ${fftw_root}
        $env{fftw_root}/lib
        $env{fftw_root}/.libs
        env fftw_root
    paths
        /usr/lib
        /usr/local/lib
    doc "fftw dynamic library"
)
